urn to more friction, in agreement with macroscopic\nmeasurements and mesoscale simulations of the friction coefficient reported in\nthe literature.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Nov 2016 08:39:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-08"}
