roach, we embed the multi-flavour Thirring model in a larger\nclass of four-fermion theories to study the chiral symmetry and its breaking in\na wider context.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Nov 2016 15:36:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-02"}
