istic frequency associated with the dielectric enhancement scales\ninversely with the square of the particle size, the major radius of the\nspheroid, and it has a weak dependence on the shape of spheroids.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Nov 2016 15:38:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-04-12"}
