g the efficiency of\ncomputational implementations and for extending applications to coarse-graining\nor multiscale molecular simulations are outlined.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 31 Oct 2016 20:39:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-03"}
