om the surface; (iii) above\nthe surface there is a \"boiling layer\" of dust with a maximum thickness of\nseveral hundred meters where the average size of the particles and their\ndensity non-monotonically depend on the altitude.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Nov 2016 13:51:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-04"}
